Karma with Jasmine:
-------------------

    - We have Two Types Of Testings.

        1. Manual Testing
            [Now a days no body using Manual Testing]

        2. Automation Testing.
            [Now a days all most all the projects using Automation Testing]

    - Karma is the Testing Framework used to perform Automation Testing on UI Applications

        Ex.
            AngularJS
            Angular4
            reactJS
            NodeJS
                --
                --
                --

     - Automation Testing categorized into 3 types.

     1. unit testing

     2. integration testing

     3. end to end testing.



1. unit testing
---------------
    - checking the perticular functionality with dummy scenarios called as unit testing.


2. integration testing
----------------------
    - checking the perticular functionality with real scenarios called as integration testing.

3. end to end testing:
---------------------
    - checking whole application with different end points (api points, physical connections) called as
      end to end testing.

Installation Of Karma
---------------------
>npm install -g karma


Testing the Controllers:
------------------------

var app = angular.module("app",[]);

app.controller("ctrl",ctrl);
function ctrl($scope){
    $scope.var_one ="Welcome";
}


karma.conf.js
-------------

describe("testing the controller", function(){
    var $controller;
    inject("making the availability of controllers",function(_$controller_){
        module("app");
        $controller=_$controller_;
    });
});



it("unit test case one",function(){
    var result = $controller.get("ctrl",{$scope:$scope});
    expect(result).equalsTo("Welcome")
        /*******Unit Test Case Success*********/

    /*****Test case fail*******/
});


>karma start


Testing the Services:
---------------------
var app = angular.module("app",[]);

app.service("my_service",my_service);
function my_service(){
   this.my_fun = function(){
        return ["Hello_1","Hello_2","Hello_3","Hello_4","Hello_5"];
   };
};


describe("testing the services",function(){
    var testServices;
    inject("testing of my_fun",function(injector){
        module("app");
        testServices = injector;
    });
});

it("unit test case one",function(){
    var testServices = testServices.get("my_service");
    var array = testServices.my_fun();

    array.contains("Hello_1");
    array.contains("Hello_2");
    array.contains("Hello_3");
    array.contains("Hello_4");
    array.contains("Hello_5");
    array.equalsTo(5);
        /******Unit Test Case Success*****/

    /****Test Case Fail*****/
});

>karma start

